{"tid":486609,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金正男背包藏12瓶解毒劑","createTime":"2017-12-02T04:26:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-02T05:08:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d596c995220d2629b331c4ea78c9ed3edacee381","tid":486609,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T04:26:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20171202/20232226\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171202%2F20232226&d=GAyoW2IVBjKVGnhFwJyaoKS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=72312bb3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171202%2F20232226&h=34097bfc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20171202/20232226</a><br />\n<br />\n金正男背包藏12瓶解毒劑<br />\n<br />\n國際新聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171202/large/17922532.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171202%2Flarge%2F17922532.jpg&h=642cb48e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n金正男<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n北韓領袖金正恩兄長金正男在馬來西亞遭塗料VX神經毒劑毒殺案，原來事發當日金正男的背包內竟有12瓶解毒劑，似預知會受神經毒劑襲擊。<br />\n<br />\n案件昨日在吉隆坡法院續審，有被告辯護律師引述毒藥專家夏爾米拉本周的供詞，指事後大馬警方送了案中多件證物給她化驗，包括12個藏有藥物的小瓶，經化驗證實是解毒劑「阿托品」（Atropine）。「阿托品」常用於治療神經毒劑中毒，其中包括VX神經毒劑。案中印尼籍被告艾莎的辯護律師指說，金正男隨身攜帶阿托品的「動機和原因，可能永遠無法證實」。艾莎和越南籍女子段詩香被控今年2月13日在吉隆坡國際機場毒殺金正男，在他面上塗上VX神經毒劑，但二人否認控罪，堅稱她們只是被騙行事，以為只是電視台惡作劇。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/法新社"},{"pid":"aee87bcfda2d430c49b730c419227bb0b71e26b2","tid":486609,"uid":54368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T05:04:13.000Z","msg":"慘, 明明係長男, 但因為係庶出所以無得繼承皇位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似睇緊古代宮廷劇咁<br />\n如果佢做皇帝, 可能北韓改革開放緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f48cb682e8546f2b406e642dc24db3af6f16f36","tid":486609,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T05:08:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>慘, 明明係長男, 但因為係庶出所以無得繼承皇位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似睇緊古代宮廷劇咁<br />\n如果佢做皇帝, 可能北韓改革開放緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能會引入真迪士尼樂園<br />\n咁就唔洗用假護照去日本玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}